text: inezīyami kebefītachewi āgerītuni menorīya yadereguti iminetinimi yelemeduti wede’inerisu yetesededutini sewochi yiwedalu፡፡ (sidetenyochu) keteset’utimi negeri belibochachewi wisit’i k’irētani āyagenyumi፡፡ be’inerisu layi chigiri bīnoribachewimi benefisochachewi layi lēlawini yimerit’alu፡፡ yenefisunimi nifigeti yemīt’ebek’i sewi inezīya inesu minyotachewini āginyīwochi nachewi፡፡
